@startuml
skinparam dpi 300
title Checkout Order

start
:initiate checkout;
note right : Step 1 - Customer initiates the checkout process
:Verify login status;
note right : Step 2 - System verifies that the customer is logged in
if (User logged in?) then (no)
    :Redirect to Login Form;
    note right : Step 3a - Customer is redirected to the Login Form
    stop
else (yes)
endif
:Check cart contents;
note right : Step 3b - System checks that the cart is not empty
if(Cart is empty?) then (yes)
    :Display "Cart is empty" error;
    note right : Step 4a - System displays a cart empty error message
    stop
else (no)
endif
:Display order summary;
note right : Step 4b - System displays order summary with items and total price
:Confirm order;
note right : Step 5 - Customer confirms the order
:Create order record;
note right : Step 6 - System creates a new order record
:Clear cart;
note right : Step 7 - System clears the customer's cart
:Display order confirmation;
note right : Step 8 - System displays order confirmation to the customer
stop

@enduml